// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2539 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: ca7f34a3-5972-50f7-ae9a-7e49e6c3c2e9

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:5* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6* OR ImageFileName = *redhat/ubi9:*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
